# @SuppressWarnings FORMATTING

## RULE
Comment BEFORE annotation, annotation on single line

## CORRECT FOR ONE
```java
// Comment explaining WHY
@SuppressWarnings("PMD.RuleName")
```

## CORRECT FOR SEVERAL
```java
@SuppressWarnings({
    // Comment explaining WHY
    "PMD.Rule1",
    // Comment explaining WHY
    "PMD.Rule2"
})
```

